It's a simple app for travel request.

1) As requestor, If you fill info in the Travel_Request Form & submit it successfully, 
   your travel request will be sent to your manager. you can receive the related feedback mail
   when the manager approved, rejected or postponed your request.

2) As manager, you will receive your member's request email, and response your member's request by clicking
   the url in your email. Once the manager feedbacked the request, the info will be sent to the requestor,
   functional manager & admin.

)3 As admin, you can receive request email & manager's feedback email, and you can maniplulate the related
   request record in the admin page, or config the mail settings.

Any problems, send mail to weizhou@redhat.com plz.
2012-09-24
